OL,3,CCritical incident declared at two
OL,4,Chospitals due to 'greater demands'
OL,6,FA critical incident has been declared
OL,7,Fafter experiencing "greater demands"
OL,8,Fin the last 24 hours.
OL,10,FIt means some routine care is being
OL,11,Fcancelled in order to increase
OL,12,Fcapacity for urgent emergency care at
OL,13,FRoyal Stoke University Hospital and
OL,14,FCounty Hospital in Stafford.
OL,16,FThe wait time for non-life-threatening
OL,17,Fconditions is said to be "longer
OL,18,Fdelays than usual" at A&E departments.
