OL,3,CCritical incident declared at two
OL,4,Chospitals due to 'greater demands'
OL,6,FPeople are being advised to only
OL,7,Fattend the hospital for a life-
OL,8,Fthreatening illness or injury, and to
OL,9,Fcollect friends or relatives "as soon
OL,10,Fas possible" if they are ready for
OL,11,Fdischarge.
OL,13,FIn a statement, the University
OL,14,FHospitals of North Midlands medical
OL,15,Fdirector, Dr Matthew Lewis said: "We
OL,16,Fare currently experiencing extremely
OL,17,Fhigh demand for all our services.
