OL,3,CCritical incident declared at two
OL,4,Chospitals due to 'greater demands'
OL,6,F"Both Royal Stoke University Hospital
OL,7,Fand County Hospital in Stafford have
OL,8,Fbeen under severe and sustained
OL,9,Fpressure since the start of the year,
OL,10,Fbut we have seen even greater demands
OL,11,Fin the last 24 hours.
OL,13,F"We have therefore taken the decision
OL,14,Fto declare a critical incident. This
OL,15,Fhelps us to take additional measures
OL,16,Fto maintain safe services for our
OL,17,Fpatients.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
