OL,3,CCritical incident declared at two
OL,4,Chospitals due to 'greater demands'
OL,6,F"Locally, we are working with our NHS
OL,7,Fand local authority partners to ensure
OL,8,Fthat people who need hospital and
OL,9,Femergency care can get treatment
OL,10,Fquickly and to identify any additional
OL,11,Fsupport that allows us to discharge
OL,12,Fpatients who do not require acute
OL,13,Fhospital care.
OL,15,F"As anticipated, the pressure is
OL,16,Fgreatest in our emergency departments,
OL,17,Fwhich are facing continued challenges
OL,18,Fas patients cannot be admitted to beds
OL,19,Fpromptly.
