OL,3,CCritical incident declared at two
OL,4,Chospitals due to 'greater demands'
OL,6,F"During this time the emergency
OL,7,Fdepartments will continue to see the
OL,8,Fsickest patients first, which means,
OL,9,Ffor some patients, there may be much
OL,10,Flonger delays than usual.
OL,12,F"We continue to ask the public to help
OL,13,Fus by only using A&E in a serious or
OL,14,Flife threatening emergency. When we're
OL,15,Fdischarging patients, we ask that
OL,16,Ftheir friends or loved ones pick them
OL,17,Fup from hospital as soon as possible
OL,18,Fand have everything they need at home."
